The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Bengal | Ghatak film
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   Ghatak film
                            
	New Delhi, Sept. 11: CPM leader Brinda Karat will inaugurate the screening of a documentary on Ritwik Ghatak here tomorrow.         
	Bengal finance minister Asim Dasgupta will attend the screening at Bangla Sanskriti Bhavan at 5.30pm. Documenting Agony: Ritwik is written by Shauvik Basu and directed by Debjani Halder.                                                                                                                                                                          
